{"tid":1193303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武派 調虎離山 打突撃咪得囉","createTime":"2019-06-08T23:59:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T04:09:10.000Z","uid":244332,"like":50,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"107d0e6222ab48d9e164cdcacc896b9404283e00","tid":1193303,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T23:59:05.000Z","msg":"去遊行搞勇武 又會俾自己友阻住哂<br />\n<br />\n警察又去哂遊行度<br />\n<br />\n和平遊行 同 勇武 根本就應該<span style=\"color: red;\">互相配合</span>"},{"pid":"6e17928df1d56e9db7a03a0a012c8f553cade4f9","tid":1193303,"uid":41389,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:00:04.000Z","msg":"-遊行起點：銅鑼灣維多利亞公園中央草坪 （維園草地）<br />\n-遊行路線：維園草地起點&gt;高士威道&gt; 禮頓道&gt;伊榮街&gt;邊寧頓街&gt;軒尼詩道西行車路&gt;金鐘道&gt;樂禮街&gt;夏愨道&gt;添美道&gt;立法會外行人路終點<br />\n-集合時間：2：30PM<br />\n-起步時間：3：00PM（或維園草地達八成滿）<br />\n-衝定唔衝，自己執生<br />\n-記得宗旨：不散<br />\n<br />\n溫和：<br />\n<strong>【長期置頂】69反送中遊行須知整合</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191837/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[懶人包] 第一次參加遊行的常見疑問Q&amp;A</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1186623/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【極重要】69遊行記得帶防Rfid卡套</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1190797/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n勇武： <br />\n<strong>食放題須知，全部資料，一世受用</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1191403/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>[law撚］被捕人仕須知</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1189300/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>［抗爭手冊］End game前準備</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1169374/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黑色三毛特別警告信號現正生效 6月8日16時</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">表示連登 facebook 網絡廣泛地區已錄得或預料會有每秒三毛回覆量超過100次/禁100次正評的網絡分化攻勢，且攻勢可能持續或於今晚或明朝早上升級。</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNv7C24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNv7C24.jpg&h=73f7da13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">注意事項</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>網民應注意username 同 三毛開post 目的 而非三毛post正評數量。<br />\n網民應負皮三毛post 入去屌佢老母 而毋須參與分化討論。<br />\n鍵盤戰士應努力推正經post 例如準備事項去抵擋三毛攻勢。<br />\n三毛會開一啲反共post 減低大家戒心 請細心思考現時網絡上所有言論。<br />\n一般市民應少上連登 關電視 而休養等待今午遊行。<br />\n鬼得一隻 林奠 其他完全唔重要 。</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZB4gyv7.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZB4gyv7.gif&h=7cacc0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a6206a497f187fdf85a84771f55df1cc080ce6f","tid":1193303,"uid":242630,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:20:52.000Z","msg":"班撚樣得把死人口，咪又係跟隊尾然後散水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50e8f56c07afa84f3395fa99856fee1605ce930","tid":1193303,"uid":244332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a6206a497f187fdf85a84771f55df1cc080ce6f","tid":1193303,"uid":242630,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:20:52.000Z","msg":"班撚樣得把死人口，咪又係跟隊尾然後散水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72992e2a2593fc55a88844e1e6b65e0e9ad1649e","tid":1193303,"uid":43061,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:32:33.000Z","msg":"你估下有幾多個真係勇武？ <br />\n加上佢地口中既勇武 隨時係屌黑警幾下老母就叫勇武"},{"pid":"49ddd36f86ac74a6fe7b7ee011b86d90bebe5616","tid":1193303,"uid":35746,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T00:33:29.000Z","msg"